reviewText: This collection of Atomfilms Shorts is a must have.  It contains two of my favorite shorts this side of Spike and Mike... Wheelchair Rebecca and Black XXX-mas.  If you like the sick and twisted stuff, you'll LOVE this.

This collection from Atom has some of the best edgy shorts this side of Spike and Mike.  Wheelchair Rebecca, Titler, American Pi and my favorite--Black xxx-mas, a modern Little Red Riding Hood that you HAVE to see. BUY IT!
